name:           cctt
version:        0.1.0.0
description:    Experiments on high-performance evaluation for cubical type theories
category:       Language
homepage:       https://github.com/AndrasKovacs/cctt#readme
bug-reports:    https://github.com/AndrasKovacs/cctt/issues
author:         Andr치s Kov치cs
